                    "effect": "Shards of sharpened glass violently shoot out from the magical banner into the newly opened wounds of a nearby enemy. The magical banner deals 1d4 persistent bleed damage to any enemy within the banner\u2019s aura that has been dealt damage since the end of your last turn.",
